{"tid":2447152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"力保中資工廠  緬軍打死22人  中國使館:制止暴力，依法查處涉事者","createTime":"2021-03-15T04:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T13:00:01.000Z","uid":227801,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7c39fdbe321a433cfcd272c08911a851e22be396","tid":2447152,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:19:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580580-20210315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580580-20210315.htm&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=8564cfad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580580-20210315.htm&h=3fed613a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580580-20210315.htm</a><br />\n緬甸的反軍事政變示威浪潮有惡化跡象，有監察團體說，星期日有最少38名示威者死亡，其中22人在最大城市仰光一個工業區內，被當局殺死。<br />\n<br />\n仰光工業區有中資工廠被縱火破壞，保安部隊開槍驅散，當局決定在兩個地區實施戒嚴，由軍方負責行使行政和司法權力。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐緬甸大使館表示，多間中資工廠被不法分子打砸搶燒，性質十分惡劣，多名中方人員受傷，有員工亦一度被困，要求緬方採取措施，制止暴力行為，依法查處涉事者，確保中國企業和人員的生命財產安全。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方發動政變後，有示威者認為，中國支持緬甸軍方，當地反華情緒日漸升高。"},{"pid":"c47c9a7a1018d5faea4d9b1d000ae4b4c2ab26c7","tid":2447152,"uid":119232,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"打自己國民<br />\n保護外國資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410ceff5f69d289a2e2a8c35bb2fef12b28022cd","tid":2447152,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你中國響聯合國反對譴責咩, 係咁架啦!"},{"pid":"c9410f5ee06c9215b9a289f7756a281bd756f12e","tid":2447152,"uid":17443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"顏色革命的影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5740887734d7a05ea0c5ee139b9c82810a60f213","tid":2447152,"uid":269202,"like":3,"dis